title: Studio To The Streets: The Hammer
description:
In this new "Studio To The Streets" episode, Jim Greco takes his signature Hammer out of the clean SUPRA studio environment and gets busy with it in the street—where it belongs. 

"It's basically a wino that takes impact," Jim said about his new shoe. "And that's what we created with the Hammer: it's the lightest, most simple shoe, that takes the most impact."
